---

## ğŸ§  Key Concepts

* Use of `va_list`, `va_start`, `va_arg`, and `va_end`
* Manual number-to-string conversion in arbitrary bases
* Handling edge cases in formatting (null strings, pointer alignment)
* Clean modular code separation

